^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Let's discuss the opening lead. Given Jenny decided to lead a spade rather than a club which is reasonable, given her nice spades. The best lead from a 3-card sequence or broken sequence is the top of the sequence. Typical sequences are KQJ or KQ10, QJ10 or QJ9, and J109 or J108.|
