NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|From all those sequence the correct lead is the top of the sequence. Jenny's lead should have been the @SK. BTW, the lead of the K asks partner to give attitude, so with any honor, partner should play a high card. So West should play the S6 (low) on the @SK.|
